## Make a payment

> Sample Request

```json
{
  "apiKey": "<%= config.auth %>",
  "billId": "566595c8ce88ccec69328566"
}
```

> 400 Response

```json
{
  "message": "Please provide a billId to make a payment for."
}
```

Make a payment towards this company's outstanding balance.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/payment/make`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`billId` | Unbill bill ID.

### Returns

Returns a `200` status code if a payment is successfully scheduled. Returns an error otherwise.